[
    {
        "source_sentence": "極樂願文",
        "translation": "written vow of ultimate bliss",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "清字經館行走福佑寺達喇嘛",
        "translation": "Dar lama of Fuyusi Temple walking in the Qingzi jingkan",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b25_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嘠卜楚薩木丹達爾吉譯",
        "translation": "Gupta Chos kyi mtshan dpal gyi",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　希有為眾施行無盡德",
        "translation": "there are rare and inexhaustible merits that can be attributed to all people",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b27_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　略念能令死主難遠離",
        "translation": "a moment's thought makes it difficult to part with the person who has died",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b28_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　恒觀有情如憶獨子者",
        "translation": "he who constantly observes sentient beings as he remembers his only child",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080b29_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　世尊無量壽佛前敬禮",
        "translation": "worship before the Bhagavān, the Buddha of Immeasurable Life",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c01_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　釋迦牟尼歷次中　　善所稱讚之勝境　往生極樂願文詞　　由慈悲故盡力說　善惡被重無明障　　天人命為嗔械殘　愛[糸*(索-糸+系)]縛在輪迴獄　　業水飄進三有海　病老苦浪多推蕩　　摧入死主海獸口　常為不欲苦擔壓　　無依玷辱之號哀　願與心為證見者　　導引困苦獨彌陀　觀音大勢至菩薩　　並眷屬前謹禱祈　為我等故與多劫　　曾發勝誓願莫忘　如妙翅尊行虛空　　以慈神力而降臨伏願自他三世。",
        "translation": "In Śākyamuni's chronicle, the excellent state that's well-praised is the words of the vow to be reborn in paradise. It's because of compassion that he tries his best to explain that good and evil are heavily hindered by ignorance, that human life is crippled by anger, that love [it*(so-it+tether)] is bound to the hell of transmigration, that the waters of karma drift into the sea of the three existences, that the waves of suffering of illness and old age often push against them, that they are crushed into the mouths of the sea of death, that they are constantly burdened by the pain of lack of desire, that they are saddened by the cries of disgrace, that they are willing to share their minds with someone who sees, that they will guide Avalokitêśvara, Maitreya, the Soldier of Fortune, and that they will pray before their retinue.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所緣二資糧海。",
        "translation": "The two oceans of accumulation that are the perceptual objects.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c12_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普合一力為倚。",
        "translation": "They are supported by the power of universal unity.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c12_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等臨命終時。",
        "translation": "When our lives are about to end.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c13_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "親見接引彌陀。",
        "translation": "We'll personally see the guiding Amitâbha.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c13_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二大菩薩。",
        "translation": "The two great bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c13_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "並諸眷屬圍繞現前。",
        "translation": "We were surrounded by our retinues.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c14_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時於佛眷屬生極專之至誠。",
        "translation": "At that point, our Buddha's retinue had grown extremely dedicated and sincere.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c14_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而無斷命之苦。",
        "translation": "They didn't suffer from the cessation of life.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c15_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "仍不失其信誠。",
        "translation": "They still didn't lose their faith.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c15_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "並所見境界之念。",
        "translation": "They're also mindful of the objective world they see.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c15_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "將終之時。",
        "translation": "When he's about to reach the end of his life.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c16_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八大佛子。",
        "translation": "eight great children of the Buddha.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c16_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆以神變來至。",
        "translation": "They all come in miraculous form.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c16_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "指引極樂之路。",
        "translation": "They showed them the path to paradise.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c17_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依教即往極樂勝境。",
        "translation": "Relying on the teachings, they then went to the paramount state of paradise.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c17_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從寶蓮中。",
        "translation": "From among the jeweled lotuses.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c17_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願生大乘利根之種姓。",
        "translation": "They want to be born into a family with great vehicle and sharp faculties.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c18_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "將生之時。",
        "translation": "When he's about to be born.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切總持及諸禪定。",
        "translation": "\"He'll maintain all meditations and concentrations.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無緣道心。",
        "translation": "unconditioned mind of enlightenment ...",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無盡辯才等。",
        "translation": "inexhaustible eloquence, and so forth.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無量諸勝功德。",
        "translation": "Measureless are their excellent qualities.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具足而得。",
        "translation": "They'll be fully attained.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c20_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即承無上導師阿彌陀佛。",
        "translation": "That's when I acknowledge the unsurpassed guide Amitâbha Buddha.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c20_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "並十方諸佛菩薩。",
        "translation": "and all the buddhas and bodhisattvas in the ten directions.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c21_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉皆歡喜。",
        "translation": "They all rejoice.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c21_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願受大乘之法勅。",
        "translation": "May I accept the great vehicle's command of the Dharma.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c22_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於彼諸法之義。",
        "translation": "In the meanings of those teachings.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c22_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "剎那閒如理融通。",
        "translation": "In a moment's time, he accurately comprehends them in principle.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c22_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即乘無礙神變。",
        "translation": "He then rides the unobstructed miraculous transformation.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c23_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至方廣佛剎。",
        "translation": "He'll go to a vast array of buddha bases.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c23_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "廣行菩薩妙行。",
        "translation": "He'll conduct the bodhisattva's wondrous practices in great detail.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c23_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願悉圓滿。",
        "translation": "Their vows are all fully accomplished.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c24_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已生淨土之時。",
        "translation": "When he's already born in the Pure Land.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c25_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "起諸勇猛慈悲。",
        "translation": "He arouses all kinds of courageous compassion.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c25_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以無礙神變。",
        "translation": "With unhindered miraculous powers.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c25_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "特至穢土。",
        "translation": "He travels to the defiled land.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為諸眾生。",
        "translation": "He'll serve all sentient beings.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c26_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "各如自緣。",
        "translation": "Each one takes on his or her own conditions.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c26_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依法而教。",
        "translation": "Teaching them in accordance with the Dharma.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c26_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願悉安之於諸佛稱讚清淨之道。",
        "translation": "May they all rest in the pure path praised by the buddhas.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c26_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普行希有之行。",
        "translation": "They'll all carry out rare actions.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c27_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆速圓滿。",
        "translation": "They'll all quickly complete it.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c28_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "利益無邊眾生。",
        "translation": "May they benefit an unlimited number of sentient beings.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c28_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願皆易得佛果。",
        "translation": "May they all easily attain the Buddhahood.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0080c28_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願臨命終時　　海會繞彌陀",
        "translation": "May the ocean assemble around Amitâbha when he reaches the end of his life.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a01_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　眼前明顯見　　慈信盈我心",
        "translation": "seeing clearly before my eyes, filling my heart with compassionate faith",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　將見中陰兆　　佛子即指教",
        "translation": "about to see the signs of the intermediate aggregate, which the buddha-son then instructs",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　既生淨土已　　來化穢土眾",
        "translation": "having been born in the Pure Land, they will transform the multitude of the defiled lands",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a04_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如此勝境。",
        "translation": "This is an excellent state.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或未得生。",
        "translation": "Perhaps he hasn't yet been born.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a05_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟願生生世世。",
        "translation": "I only wish to be reborn for generations to come.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a05_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常遇佛教。",
        "translation": "I'd like to encounter Buddhism always.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a05_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在諸經論中。",
        "translation": "Among the sūtras and śāstras.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "契悟聞思修。",
        "translation": "I'll understand what I've heard, contemplate, and cultivate.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願得清淨之身。",
        "translation": "May he attain a pure body.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a06_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既得其身。",
        "translation": "Once I've attained that body.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於高類七德莊嚴。",
        "translation": "I'll adorn myself with the seven virtues of the higher types.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a08_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願不遠離。",
        "translation": "I hope I won't be far from them.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a08_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是於一切時中。",
        "translation": "Thus, at all times.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憶念前生。",
        "translation": "He'll remember past lives.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願得宿命智。",
        "translation": "\"May he attain knowledge of past lives.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生生世世。",
        "translation": "From birth to birth.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a10_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡見三有。",
        "translation": "Whenever he sees the three existences.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a10_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆生無益之心。",
        "translation": "They all give rise to a mind that's not helpful.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a10_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而於解脫功德。",
        "translation": "Instead, they give rise to thoughts of snatching at the merits of liberation.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a10_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即起奪意之念。",
        "translation": "They then give rise to thoughts of snatching their minds.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a11_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在諸佛律中。",
        "translation": "Among the Buddha's precepts, that's the desire to leave home.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a11_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願得出家。",
        "translation": "They want to leave home.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a11_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既出家之時。",
        "translation": "When he leaves home, he'll become a renunciant.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a13_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸惡墮。",
        "translation": "In the midst of all the bad rebirths ...",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a13_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毫無所染。",
        "translation": "Nothing was tainted.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a13_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "圓守禁戒。",
        "translation": "He completely observes the precepts.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a13_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行至無極門中。",
        "translation": "He'll practice until he reaches the gate of infinity.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a14_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得大菩提。",
        "translation": "He attains great enlightenment.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a14_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願如大比丘阿閦佛。",
        "translation": "May he be like the great monk Akṣobhya.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a14_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復於世世生生。",
        "translation": "Again, he'll be reborn from generation to generation.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a16_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "在染淨諸法中。",
        "translation": "Among the pure and defiled dharmas.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a16_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如理融通。",
        "translation": "He correctly interpenetrates the principle.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a16_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "圓成之道。",
        "translation": "He perfectly completes the path.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a16_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法文義。",
        "translation": "The meanings of the various dharmas.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a17_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持不失忘之總持。",
        "translation": "He maintains a commandership that's not lost or forgotten.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a17_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願悉豐足而得。",
        "translation": "May it all be fully attained.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a17_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如已所持。",
        "translation": "As he has upheld it.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "示於他時。",
        "translation": "When he shows it to others.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願得清淨無礙之辯。",
        "translation": "May he attain the clarity and unimpeded eloquence.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復於生生世世。",
        "translation": "Again, in all his lifetimes.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於楞嚴等諸定。",
        "translation": "In concentrations like that of Śūraṃgama ...",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "肉眼等五眼。",
        "translation": "The five eyes, such as the physical eye, and the six powers, such as the mental object.",
        "source": "T19n0935_001:0081a20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "神境等六通。",
